descriptionHTML:
What dessert comes to mind that starts with the letter N? Nutella!

Or maybe Nerds!

Nougat?!

There's so many options! This watchface automatically cycles through over a dozen of your favorite M desserts throughout the day!

FEATURES
- Watchface
- Daydream
- Muzei Wallpaper
- Works on Android Wear, Android TV, phones, and tablets
comments: Sweet Like it! Can't seem to change from M deserts though
recentChanges: - With the pre-release of N, the app now shows users a variety of N desserts by default (graphical branding will change soon)
- Watchface uses the new Hourglass library
